859
00:46:25,460 --> 00:46:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] pa kažu, ali to baš mora biti onako kako ja hoću.

860
00:46:29,219 --> 00:46:31,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da ima dođen tip karaktera,

861
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji je vrlo originan i jednostavno,

862
00:46:33,619 --> 00:46:35,360
[SPEAKER_01] oni znaju šta je ispravno.

863
00:46:35,360 --> 00:46:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] To su oni snimači ratnih filmova?

864
00:46:37,719 --> 00:46:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nisu.

865
00:46:38,980 --> 00:46:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu, ok.

866
00:46:39,780 --> 00:46:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] To su, ajmo reći, ljudi koji su skloni perfekcionizmu,

867
00:46:42,840 --> 00:46:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji imaju izjedno visoke standarde u sebi.

868
00:46:45,300 --> 00:46:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] Obično su tehničke struke.

869
00:46:46,500 --> 00:46:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] Znači oni točno znaju što je ispravno.

870
00:46:50,400 --> 00:46:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, kako bi to rekao, što si rigidniji, ok.

871
00:46:58,119 --> 00:47:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] To u principu, to je sve interesantno.

872
00:47:00,239 --> 00:47:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mi smo mogli pričati puno o tome,

873
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:06,860
[SPEAKER_01] ali recimo, koja razlika mi će biti prilagodljiv i fleksibilan?

874
00:47:06,860 --> 00:47:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] Objasnite mi.

875
00:47:08,579 --> 00:47:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] Prilagodljen, znači vrlo često korespondira sa biti indoktriniran.

876
00:47:14,440 --> 00:47:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] Daću primjer, recimo, ako ja odlučim, a nemam veze s tim,

877
00:47:18,320 --> 00:47:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, na putu sam i želim ući u neku džamiju.

878
00:47:20,539 --> 00:47:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam musliman.

879
00:47:22,619 --> 00:47:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, zanimav je vidjeti kako to izgleda.

880
00:47:25,039 --> 00:47:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nekak je kulturno pitaš, prije što uđeš,

881
00:47:27,059 --> 00:47:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi se trebao obući, što je prikladno što ne prikladno,

882
00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi se trebao ponašati.

883
00:47:30,539 --> 00:47:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ušao sam unutra, razgledao sam to sve skupa,

884
00:47:33,340 --> 00:47:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] ispoštivao sam različitosti,

885
00:47:35,159 --> 00:47:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] zašto sam van, skinuo sam se, ja sam ponovo svoj.

886
00:47:37,440 --> 00:47:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja sam bio fleksibilan.

887
00:47:39,519 --> 00:47:41,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ušao sam, kužemo,

888
00:47:41,059 --> 00:47:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] međutim, ostao sam svoj.

889
00:47:43,260 --> 00:47:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] Biti plagodljiv je vrlo često

890
00:47:44,880 --> 00:47:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] direktno vezan za indoktrinaciju.

891
00:47:47,019 --> 00:47:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] I nastavno, njihovi stavovi postoje moji stavovi.

892
00:47:49,159 --> 00:47:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto sam van, više nisam svoj.

893
00:47:51,340 --> 00:47:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo često to problem je

894
00:47:53,320 --> 00:47:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu, u vezama,

895
00:47:54,579 --> 00:47:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] gdje zapravo dvoje ljudi,

896
00:47:56,679 --> 00:47:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] da, dijele taj mi osjećaj,

897
00:47:58,599 --> 00:48:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja ostajem ja, vi ostajete vi,

898
00:48:00,900 --> 00:48:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi smo zajedno.

899
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:04,760
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, kad se počnemo stapati u nešto,

900
00:48:04,760 --> 00:48:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo gubimo vlastit identitet.

901
00:48:06,840 --> 00:48:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kad počnemo misliti tuđim mozgom.

902
00:48:09,039 --> 00:48:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] Preprilagodljivost, dajmo reći.

903
00:48:10,579 --> 00:48:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] I to uvijek rezultira katastrofom.

904
00:48:13,880 --> 00:48:15,639
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mislim, uvijek.

905
00:48:15,639 --> 00:48:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] A tamo je često.

906
00:48:17,280 --> 00:48:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jel da?

907
00:48:17,980 --> 00:48:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

908
00:48:18,300 --> 00:48:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] Što ako jedan od partnera ima neku ovisnost?

909
00:48:21,880 --> 00:48:23,280
[SPEAKER_00] Naprimjer, ne znam, kockanje,

910
00:48:23,280 --> 00:48:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] alkohol, droga.

911
00:48:24,980 --> 00:48:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jako interesantno.

912
00:48:26,460 --> 00:48:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] Suštinski svi smo ovisni.

913
00:48:27,960 --> 00:48:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

914
00:48:29,639 --> 00:48:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo.

915
00:48:31,039 --> 00:48:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kad kaže da smo ovisni,

916
00:48:33,059 --> 00:48:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] o nekoj drogi.

917
00:48:35,420 --> 00:48:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, droga je substitut.

918
00:48:37,460 --> 00:48:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nismo ovisni o drogi.

919
00:48:38,920 --> 00:48:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo ovisni o emociji koje ta droga zaziva.

920
00:48:40,880 --> 00:48:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] Kod nam ona daje.

921
00:48:41,559 --> 00:48:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

922
00:48:42,320 --> 00:48:47,780
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, svatko, netko može biti ovisan o dobroti.

923
00:48:47,780 --> 00:48:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno, moram raditi.

924
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad god je nešto podmorati, kompulzivno,

925
00:48:51,480 --> 00:48:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] e pa to je ovisnost.

926
00:48:52,860 --> 00:48:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, i rad može biti ovisnost.

927
00:48:56,820 --> 00:48:57,340
[SPEAKER_01] Uspjeh.

928
00:48:57,340 --> 00:48:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] Aha.

929
00:48:57,980 --> 00:48:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] U redu.

930
00:48:58,900 --> 00:49:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, neki se pikaju sa uspjehom.

931
00:49:00,559 --> 00:49:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] Neki se pikaju sa srećom, pa su hedonisti.

932
00:49:03,980 --> 00:49:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] Neki se pikaju sa moći.

933
00:49:05,960 --> 00:49:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] Neki se pikaju sa strahom.

934
00:49:08,340 --> 00:49:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] Neki se pikaju sa tugom.

935
00:49:11,300 --> 00:49:12,860
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, toka što smo pričali malo prije,

936
00:49:12,860 --> 00:49:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo Šekspir rekao da živo teatora,

937
00:49:15,119 --> 00:49:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] a mi samo glumci u tom životnom teatru.

938
00:49:17,860 --> 00:49:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, teatru naših roditelja.

939
00:49:20,000 --> 00:49:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, svatko od nas, to je bilo zgodno,

940
00:49:22,539 --> 00:49:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] znači, međugledatelji pitaju,

941
00:49:25,980 --> 00:49:27,820
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi došlo, to smo bili spominjali,

942
00:49:27,820 --> 00:49:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] znači, neki poznati redatelji snimeo film

943
00:49:31,239 --> 00:49:34,739
[SPEAKER_01] o vašem životu, kojeg žanra bi bio taj film.

944
00:49:34,739 --> 00:49:36,719
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, neki snimaju drame,

945
00:49:36,719 --> 00:49:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] naravno je skupljato u tugu,

946
00:49:38,900 --> 00:49:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] neko snima trilere.

947
00:49:40,440 --> 00:49:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja hoću reći, jako je bitno osvijestiti

948
00:49:42,260 --> 00:49:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] i, ajmo reći, u konačnici,

949
00:49:44,400 --> 00:49:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] pre sad biti glumac

950
00:49:45,639 --> 00:49:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] i postati scenarista, redatelji,

951
00:49:47,980 --> 00:49:49,179
[SPEAKER_01] producent svog života.

952
00:49:49,179 --> 00:49:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] A taj život bi trebao nositi

953
00:49:51,300 --> 00:49:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] nekako ime sreća.

954
00:49:54,019 --> 00:49:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, sreću svatko doživljava

955
00:49:56,099 --> 00:49:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] na svoj način.

956
00:49:57,159 --> 00:49:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam da se čovjek osjeća

957
00:49:58,780 --> 00:49:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] da ima taj unutarnji mir,

958
00:49:59,980 --> 00:50:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] da ima unutarnji balans,

959
00:50:01,300 --> 00:50:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] da se osjeća ispunjen.

960
00:50:02,460 --> 00:50:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ne je nužno sreća.

961
00:50:03,780 --> 00:50:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] Zadovoljstvo je puno bolja stvar.

962
00:50:05,420 --> 00:50:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi onda bila formula

963
00:50:07,519 --> 00:50:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] za sreću za svakog od nas?

964
00:50:09,019 --> 00:50:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da to sad zvuči

965
00:50:10,519 --> 00:50:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] onako bezveze na postavljeno pitanje.

966
00:50:12,840 --> 00:50:14,139
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala je pisao pjesme o tome

967
00:50:14,139 --> 00:50:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] koji je puno sreće.

968
00:50:15,119 --> 00:50:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, svatko sreću

969
00:50:17,800 --> 00:50:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] definira drugačije.

970
00:50:18,940 --> 00:50:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Je jedna od velikih stvari

971
00:50:22,960 --> 00:50:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] koje treba naučiti

972
00:50:24,280 --> 00:50:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] da ono što tražimo izvana

973
00:50:25,460 --> 00:50:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] trebamo naći u sebi.

974
00:50:26,539 --> 00:50:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] Oni koji ganje uspjeh

975
00:50:28,340 --> 00:50:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo žele biti

976
00:50:29,940 --> 00:50:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] i osjećati se vrijedni,

977
00:50:30,760 --> 00:50:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] ponosni na sebi,

978
00:50:31,599 --> 00:50:32,639
[SPEAKER_01] a zapravo treba shvatiti

979
00:50:32,639 --> 00:50:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] da oni jesu takvi

980
00:50:33,760 --> 00:50:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] samim tim što postoje.

981
00:50:35,239 --> 00:50:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da oni koji traži dobrotu,

982
00:50:37,059 --> 00:50:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] raditi dobre stvari,

983
00:50:38,159 --> 00:50:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] da zapravo treba prihvatiti

984
00:50:39,840 --> 00:50:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] da oni jesu dobri ljudi,

985
00:50:40,980 --> 00:50:42,780
[SPEAKER_01] da ne moraju dokazivati dobrotu.

986
00:50:42,780 --> 00:50:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da ljudi koji ganjaju sreću

987
00:50:45,539 --> 00:50:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] da trebaju shvatiti

988
00:50:46,780 --> 00:50:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] da oni jesu sreća.

989
00:50:48,820 --> 00:50:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da nemoju to tražiti izvana.

990
00:50:50,380 --> 00:50:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] A to je zapravo ono

991
00:50:53,280 --> 00:50:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] čim se ja bavim.

992
00:50:54,159 --> 00:50:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] Moj posao je da identificiram,

993
00:50:56,139 --> 00:50:57,199
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

994
00:50:57,199 --> 00:50:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] software koji imate,

995
00:50:58,179 --> 00:50:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] da ga upgradeamo

996
00:50:59,300 --> 00:51:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] i da zapravo budete

997
00:51:00,940 --> 00:51:02,440
[SPEAKER_01] puno bolja verzija sebe.

998
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ne samo za sebe,

999
00:51:03,880 --> 00:51:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] nego i za partnera,

1000
00:51:05,059 --> 00:51:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] za djecu,

1001
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:07,199
[SPEAKER_01] za svijet oko nas.

1002
00:51:07,199 --> 00:51:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] I što onda sad danas

1003
00:51:10,019 --> 00:51:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad naši gledatelji

1004
00:51:11,239 --> 00:51:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] ovo sad pogledaju,

1005
00:51:12,920 --> 00:51:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] poslušaju,

1006
00:51:13,619 --> 00:51:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] promisle,

1007
00:51:14,260 --> 00:51:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] pitaju se

1008
00:51:15,500 --> 00:51:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji film ja snimam,

1009
00:51:17,019 --> 00:51:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] što ćemo im na kraju reći?

1010
00:51:18,800 --> 00:51:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih rekao ovako,

1011
00:51:20,559 --> 00:51:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte,

1012
00:51:21,039 --> 00:51:21,860
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1013
00:51:21,860 --> 00:51:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] nažalost,

1014
00:51:22,539 --> 00:51:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi dolaze

1015
00:51:24,079 --> 00:51:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] već kada je kasno,

1016
00:51:25,579 --> 00:51:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] kada je već razvod nastupio,

1017
00:51:27,340 --> 00:51:28,380
[SPEAKER_01] kada su toliko

1018
00:51:28,380 --> 00:51:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] tuđeni jedni od drugoga,

1019
00:51:30,000 --> 00:51:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] kada je,

1020
00:51:30,900 --> 00:51:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći,

1021
00:51:33,219 --> 00:51:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] jako narušen odnos sa dijeti,

1022
00:51:34,980 --> 00:51:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] to imali se dijeti ponašano

1023
00:51:36,179 --> 00:51:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] devijantan način,

1024
00:51:37,320 --> 00:51:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] ili kad se nas bole,

1025
00:51:40,239 --> 00:51:40,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1026
00:51:40,699 --> 00:51:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] puno kvalitetnije

1027
00:51:42,599 --> 00:51:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] prevenirati stvari,

1028
00:51:44,559 --> 00:51:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1029
00:51:45,079 --> 00:51:47,219
[SPEAKER_01] čisto informirati se,

1030
00:51:47,219 --> 00:51:50,219
[SPEAKER_01] možda biti dovoljno otvoren

1031
00:51:50,219 --> 00:51:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] i čuti neke stvari,

1032
00:51:51,960 --> 00:51:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] preispitati neke stvari.

1033
00:51:53,699 --> 00:51:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] i to je interesanto,

1034
00:51:54,420 --> 00:51:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] kada država nije definirala

1035
00:51:56,579 --> 00:51:57,340
[SPEAKER_01] zakonski,

1036
00:51:57,340 --> 00:51:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] da mora umišći na tehnički pregled,

1037
00:51:58,900 --> 00:52:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ljudi bi uopće išlo s autom.

1038
00:52:01,039 --> 00:52:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] Na tehnički.

1039
00:52:01,679 --> 00:52:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] Vozli bi ga dok se ne raspadne,

1040
00:52:03,900 --> 00:52:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] tek onda nešto.

1041
00:52:05,079 --> 00:52:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim,

1042
00:52:06,099 --> 00:52:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo je slična analogija.

1043
00:52:07,679 --> 00:52:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1044
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:10,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne želiš dovesti u riziki sebe

1045
00:52:10,639 --> 00:52:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] i druge ljude

1046
00:52:11,340 --> 00:52:12,559
[SPEAKER_01] vozići loš auto.

1047
00:52:12,559 --> 00:52:13,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tako i ovo.

1048
00:52:13,940 --> 00:52:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] Imam kolegu Zubara,

1049
00:52:16,699 --> 00:52:17,820
[SPEAKER_01] on isto tako kaže,

1050
00:52:17,820 --> 00:52:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] kod njega dođu

1051
00:52:18,619 --> 00:52:19,179
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti već,

1052
00:52:19,179 --> 00:52:20,739
[SPEAKER_01] da ne vijelim,

1053
00:52:20,739 --> 00:52:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa ona se pita,

1054
00:52:21,980 --> 00:52:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] zašto ne dođu čisto na pregled,

1055
00:52:23,239 --> 00:52:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] da vide,

1056
00:52:23,539 --> 00:52:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] pa mogu prevenirati neke stvari.

1057
00:52:25,320 --> 00:52:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je namljeno,

1058
00:52:26,119 --> 00:52:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] koji mi manje će i koštiti.

1059
00:52:27,219 --> 00:52:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kod auta

1060
00:52:29,380 --> 00:52:30,719
